word_mean_info__list.difference: 普通用词，可指中学生，但主要指高等学校或专科学校的学生。
通俗用词，指某一门学问上的初学者，尤指成年的初学者。
特指中小学生，尤其是小学生。
可指一切学生，尤指学识渊博的某一学科的学者。

list.abstract: Student.com是一个全球化的留学生公寓预订平台，免费为同学们提供海外留学租房咨询和预订服务。2016年2月，该团队已获得 6000 万美金的融资。

yingyinNormal.en: I'm the student. Isn't she cute? No.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我就是那个学生。真可爱，才怪。

yingyinNormal.en: Every year, the school has a student showcase.
yingyinNormal.zh: 学校每年一次会举办学生科技展。

yingyinNormal.en: I can't believe it. I'm officially a college student!
yingyinNormal.zh: 不可思议，我正式成为大学生了！

yingyinNormal.en: Man, we're gonna rock that Asian Student Union.
yingyinNormal.zh: 哥们儿，我们要把"亚洲学生联合会"整的惊天动地了。

yingyinNormal.en: I found another tweet from a student at Sheldon's lecture.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我又看到了一条谢尔顿课上的学生的微博。

yingyinNormal.en: What about your classes? I'm not a student anymore, Jack.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你的课怎么样了？我已经不再是这里的学生了，杰克。

yingyinNormal.en: I was always a pretty good student. You were always the smartest student in the class. That's not good enough.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我过去一直是个很好的学生，你一直是班级里最聪明的学生，这些都还不够好。

yingyinNormal.en: Don't come to Oxford as an exchange student from Taiwan and only hang out with other Chinese students.
yingyinNormal.zh: 一个学生从台湾到牛津来交换，不要只和中国学生一起。

yingyinNormal.en: There must be some way to determine who the best student is.
yingyinNormal.zh: 肯定有办法决定最棒的学生是谁。

yingyinNormal.en: Of course, who am I to argue with a check-plus student?
yingyinNormal.zh: 当然，我怎么能和得A的优秀学生争论呢?

yingyinNormal.en: To make sure that Terrance Fletcher's never allowed to do this to another student.
yingyinNormal.zh: 确保不会再有学生遭到弗莱彻的虐待。

yingyinNormal.en: As a student, I created these games as a friendly competition, but be prepared.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我在学生时代创立这些比赛作为友谊竞赛。

yingyinNormal.en: I probably look as wide-eyed, fresh and artless as any other student. But I wasn't.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我也许看上去和别的学生一样天真烂漫，可我不是。

yingyinNormal.en: We are one school, one student body, one faculty! Can we not agree on that?
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们是同一所学校，带着同一批学生的老师！这点应该都同意吧？

yingyinNormal.en: Well, you're here, and you're learning. Sure sounds like a student to me.
yingyinNormal.zh: 那么，既然你还在这里，而且你还在学习，至少听起来你还是我的学生。

yingyinNormal.en: I was in her home-ec class. And he was my best student. Yeah, she was my best teacher.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我去上她的家政课。他是我最好的学生。她是我最好的老师。

yingyinNormal.en: This money is a job we could be giving to a single mother or a student just out of school.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这笔钱，就是一份我们本可给一位单身母亲或刚毕业大学生的工作。

yingyinNormal.en: Three are Saudis? Here legally on F-1 student visas. Yasin Said was born in Michigan.
yingyinNormal.zh: 三名沙特人？他们持F1学生签证合法入境，亚辛·赛义德出生在密歇根州。

yingyinNormal.en: I mean, I mean I've been in, relationships in general, but I have never done it with a student. I mean I not, not it.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我是说我跟别人交往过，但是我没跟学生做过…不…

yingyinNormal.en: Well, how did you meet him? There's not much crossover for a national honor society student and a pork model.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你怎么认识他的？全国优秀学生跟猪排模特能有多少交集啊。

direction_info.description:
数据源自2012-2023年12年间全国考研试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2012-2023年全国考研英语一和考研英语二共24套考研试卷，包括阅读、完型填空、翻译、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选全国考研考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2012-2023年12年间全国考研英语一和考研英语二试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

sense_info_list.en: a person who is studying at a school or college

examination_example.sentence: According to the National Center for Education Statistics, nearly 80 percent of college <highlight>students</highlight> end up changing their majors at least once.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 根据国家教育统计中心的数据，近80%的大学生最终至少换过一次专业。

examination_example.sentence: Many <highlight>students</highlight> find themselves listing one major on their college applications, but switching to another after taking college classes.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 许多学生发现自己在申请大学时填写了一个专业，但在上完大学课程后就转到了另一个专业。

examination_example.sentence: For instance, one of the apps the <highlight>students</highlight> are developing suggests movies based on your mood.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 例如，学生们正在开发的一款应用程序可以根据你的情绪推荐电影。

sense_info_list.en: denoting someone who is studying in order to enter a particular profession

direction_info.description:
数据源自2018-2021年4年间全国各省市中考试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2018-2021年全国重点省市中考试卷，包括听力、阅读、完形、单选、填空、改错、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选各省市考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2018-2021年4年间全国各省市中考试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

examination_example.sentence: When she was at school, Jessica watched the other <highlight>students</highlight> on the playground.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 杰西卡上学时，在操场上看着其他学生。

examination_example.sentence: Jing Wei, 25 and Sheng Yang, 27, China: designer and graduate <highlight>student</highlight>
examination_example.sentence_trans: 25岁的景伟和27岁的杨盛（中国）：设计师和研究生。

examination_example.sentence: And he felt hatred for the <highlight>students</highlight> who did not know the value of hard work.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 他对那些不知道努力学习的价值的学生感到憎恨。
